So what do you have in your `~/.electron-gyp/.node-gyp/iojs-1.5.0/common.gypi` at around line 269?  Mine still has:

```
          ['clang==1', {
            'xcode_settings': {
              'GCC_VERSION': 'com.apple.compilers.llvm.clang.1_0',
              'CLANG_CXX_LANGUAGE_STANDARD': 'gnu++0x',  # -std=gnu++0x
            },
          }],
```

(note the missing `CLANG_CXX_LIBRARY`)

@antonycourtney mine has the following around line 387:

```python
['clang==1', {
  'xcode_settings': {
    'GCC_VERSION': 'com.apple.compilers.llvm.clang.1_0',
    'CLANG_CXX_LANGUAGE_STANDARD': 'gnu++0x',  # -std=gnu++0x
